title: Doug Miles interviews Dick Hyman January 31, 2011
description: Doug Miles interviews jazz legend Dick Hyman prior to his appearance at the Sarasota Jazz Festival Feb. 4, 2011. He also talks about being Woody Allen's musical arranger and composer on several of his films. (www.dougmilesmedia.com)
